 Post Statuses','Choose which post statuses can be accessed via shortlinks'=>'Yan awọn ipo post wo ni a le wọle si nipasẹ shortlinks','Published'=>'Ti a tẹjade','Draft'=>'Draft','Pending Review'=>'N duro de Atunwo','Private'=>'Ikọkọ','Expired Links'=>'Awọn ọna asopọ ti o ti pari','Default Expired Redirect URL'=>'URL Redirect ti o ti pari ti aiyipada','Where should expired shortlinks redirect?'=>'Nibo ni awọn shortlinks ti o ti pari yẹ ki o tọka si?','When a shortlink expires, visitors will be redirected to this URL instead of seeing an error. Leave empty to show the default expiration message.'=>'Nigbati shortlink ba ti pari, awọn alejo yoo tọka si URL yii dipo ki wọn ri aṣiṣe kan. Fi silẹ ki o le fi ifiranṣẹ ipari aiyipada han.','Revisions'=>'Revisions','Revision Link Visibility'=>'Revision Link Visibility','When enabled, revision shortlinks will appear in the "All Shortlinks" table based on the behavior you configure below.'=>'Nigbati o ba mu ṣiṣẹ, awọn shortlinks atunṣe yoo han ninu tabili "All Shortlinks" da lori ihuwasi ti o ṣe ilana ni isalẹ.','When Revision is Created'=>'Nigbati Atunṣe ti ṣẹda','When Revision is Created or Link is First Used'=>'Nigbati Atunṣe ti ṣẹda tabi ọna asopọ ti a lo ni akọkọ','Show Shortlink in Revision Table'=>'Fihan Shortlink ninu Tabili Atunṣe','Display shortlink column when viewing revisions in PublishPress Revisions.'=>'Fihan ọwọn shortlink nigbati o ba n wo awọn atunṣe ninu PublishPress Revisions.','Revision Visibility for Visitors'=>'Ifojusi Atunṣe fun Awọn Alejo','Allow logged-out visitors to view revision content via shortlinks.'=>'Jẹ ki awọn alejo ti ko forukọsilẹ wo akoonu atunṣe nipasẹ shortlinks.','By default, PublishPress Revisions blocks visitors from viewing revision previews. When enabled, revision shortlinks will render the revision content directly for logged-out visitors instead of redirecting to the preview URL.'=>'Ni aiyipada, PublishPress Revisions n ṣe idiwọ awọn alejo lati wo awọn awotẹlẹ atunṣe. Nigbati a ba mu ṣiṣẹ, awọn shortlinks atunṣe yoo gbe akoonu atunṣe taara fun awọn alejo ti ko forukọsilẹ dipo ki o yipada si URL awotẹlẹ.','Dummy'=>'Dummy','No post types configured yet. Click "Add Post Type" to get started.'=>'Ko si awọn iru ifiweranṣẹ ti a ti ṣeto sibẹsibẹ. Tẹ "Fikun-un Iru Ifiweranṣẹ" lati bẹrẹ.','Add Post Type'=>'Fikun-un Iru Ifiweranṣẹ','Log entry deleted successfully.'=>'Iwe akọọlẹ ti paarẹ ni成功成功.','%d log entries deleted successfully.'=>'%d awọn iwe akọọlẹ ti paarẹ ni成功成功.','All logs have been cleared.'=>'Gbogbo awọn iwe akọọlẹ ti nu.','Title'=>'Ak title','Details'=>'Awọn alaye','Are you sure you want to delete this log entry?'=>'Ṣe o dajudaju fẹ lati paarẹ iwe akọọlẹ yii?','Tablet'=>'Tabulẹti','Mobile'=>'Alagbeka','Desktop'=>'Tabili','%1$s from %2$s visited at %3$s'=>'%1$s lati %2$s ti ṣabẹwo ni %3$s','%1$s visited at %2$s'=>'%1$s ti ṣabẹwo ni %2$s','From %1$s, visited at %2$s'=>'Lati %1$s, ti ṣabẹwo ni %2$s','Visited at %s'=>'Bí a ṣe bẹ̀rẹ̀ ní %s','via %s'=>'nípasẹ̀ %s','Edit shortlink settings'=>'Ṣatunkọ́ àtúnṣe ìjápọ̀','Target url not found.'=>'Àdírẹsì àfojúsùn kò rí.','Invalid URL scheme. Only http, https, ftp, ftps, and mailto are allowed.'=>'Àtúnṣe àdírẹsì URL kò tọ́. Kánkán http, https, ftp, ftps, àti mailto ni a gba laaye.','Invalid URL.'=>'Àdírẹsì URL kò tọ́.','Tiny slug could not created.'=>'Kò le dá tiny slug silẹ.','Link - %s'=>'Ìjápọ̀ - %s','Shortlink will appear here'=>'Ìjápọ̀ kékèké yóò hàn nibi','Enter a long URL and make a shortlink'=>'Tẹ̀ àdírẹsì URL gígùn kan kí o sì dá ìjápọ̀ kékèké silẹ','Long URL'=>'Àdírẹsì URL gígùn','Close'=>'Pẹ̀yà','Create Shortlink'=>'Dá ìjápọ̀ kékèké silẹ','Reset Today\'s Analytics'=>'Tun ìtàn ọjọ́ yìí ṣe àtúnṣe','Reset Week\'s Analytics'=>'Tun ìtàn ọ̀sẹ̀ yìí ṣe àtúnṣe','Reset Month\'s Analytics'=>'Tun ìtàn oṣù yìí ṣe àtúnṣe','Reset Year\'s Analytics'=>'Tun ìtàn ọdún yìí ṣe àtúnṣe','Are you sure you want to reset the analytics for this period? This action cannot be undone.'=>'Ṣé o dájú pé o fẹ́ tun ìtàn àlàyé fún àkókò yìí ṣe àtúnṣe? Iṣe yìí kò le yọ.','Today'=>'Òní','Last 7 Days'=>'Ọjọ́ 7 to kọja','Last 1 Month'=>'Oṣù 1 to kẹhin','Last 1 Year'=>'Ọdun 1 to kẹhin','If you like %1$s please leave us a %2$s rating. Thank you!'=>'Ti o ba fẹ %1$s jọwọ fi wa silẹ %2$s akọsilẹ. O ṣeun!','About'=>'Nipa','Documentation'=>'Iwe-ẹkọ','Contact'=>'Kan si','Download QR Code'=>'Gbe QR Koodu silẹ','We have developed extensions for the below browsers.'=>'A ti ṣe agbekalẹ awọn itẹsiwaju fun awọn aṣawakiri ti o wa ni isalẹ.','Click on your preferred one to Download the extension.'=>'Tẹ lori eyi ti o fẹ julọ lati gba itẹsiwaju silẹ.','Download the Extension'=>'Gba Itẹsiwaju silẹ','Need PublishPress Shortlinks Support?'=>'Ṣe o nilo Atilẹyin Awọn ọna asopọ Kukuru PublishPress?','If you need help or have a new feature request, let us know.'=>'Ti o ba nilo iranlọwọ tabi ni ibeere ẹya tuntun, jẹ ki a mọ.','Request Support'=>'Beere Atilẹyin','Detailed documentation is also available on the plugin website.'=>'Iwe-ẹkọ alaye tun wa lori oju opo wẹẹbu plugin.','View Knowledge Base'=>'Wo Ibi Ẹkọ','This plugin can be deleted.'=>'Plugin yii le parẹ.','Copied.'=>'Ti a daakọ.']];